name: Darkhorse Analytics
tag_list: quantitative, analytics, business-intelligence, optimization-models, emergency-services, decision-support, canadian-company
overview: Darkhorse Analytics is a quantitative consulting firm that specializes in analytics, data visualization, geo-spatial analysis, forecasting, and optimization modeling. Darkhorse provides consulting services and business intelligence solutions to health, transportation, resource, and manufacturing industries; and to federal, state and provincial governments across North America.
